Package store.business.gui.view

Class NewClientView

  • java.lang.Object
    • store.business.gui.view.NewClientView
  • public class NewClientView
extends java.lang.Object

    The view for creating a new client

    The public class NewClientView class is a view for creating a new client. It sets a locker in order to we can't start a second instance of this view at the same time.
